        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Withnoidea/images/main/20250918221106.png" alt="20250918221106"></p><h1 id="fare-thee-well-dinks-song">Fare Thee Well (Dink’s Song)</h1><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function">Fare Thee <span class="title">Well</span> <span class="params">(Dink<span class="string">'s Song) - Oscar Isaac/Marcus Mumford</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="params"><span class="function"></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="params"><span class="function">If I had wings like Noah'</span>s dove</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params"><span class="function"></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params"><span class="function">I<span class="string">'d fly the river to the one I love</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="params"><span class="function"></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="params"><span class="function">Fare thee well my honey fare thee well</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="params"><span class="function"></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="params"><span class="function">Well I had a man who was long and tall</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="params"><span class="function"></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="params"><span class="function">Who moved his body like a cannon ball</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="params"><span class="function"></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="params"><span class="function">Fare thee well my honey fare thee well</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="params"><span class="function"></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="params"><span class="function">I remember one evening in the pouring rain</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="params"><span class="function"></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="params"><span class="function">In my heart was an aching pain</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="params"><span class="function"></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="params"><span class="function">Fare thee well my honey fare thee well</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="params"><span class="function"></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="params"><span class="function">Bloody river was muddy and wild</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="params"><span class="function"></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="params"><span class="function">Can'</span>t give a bloody <span class="keyword">for</span> my unborn child</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params"><span class="function"></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params"><span class="function">Fare thee well my honey fare thee well</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params"><span class="function"></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params"><span class="function">Sure as a bird flying high above</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params"><span class="function"></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params"><span class="function">Life ain<span class="string">'t worth living without the one you love</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="params"><span class="function"></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="params"><span class="function">Fare thee well my honey fare thee well</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="params"><span class="function"></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"><span class="params"><span class="function">Fare thee well my honey fare thee well</span></span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
